name: Collar sewing kit
description:
CLAUDINE & COMPAGNIE has teamed up with illustrator Lucille Michieli to create this beautiful hand screen printed kit for you to make your own collar. The kit is composed of cotton linen mix and printed fabric for you to make the collar, buttons and the beautifully illustrated instructions. You will also find your very own 'claudine & compagnie - made by me' label to sew on once your collar is finished. The lovely hand screen linen kit bag can then be used to store your collar. This is a very simple collar to make and is suitable for beginners. Instructions are also in french. Needle and thread are not included. The kit does not include the finished collar.

Download our step by step instructions PDF
